    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble demonstrates excellent agreement with N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories for all three QoIs, with E/uval well below 1.96 and QoI differences below 2% in all cases. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed; test conditions achieved level 2 against a required level 3, which the team accepted given the prescriptive nature of ASTM F1717. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
